[DQC.US.0087.9371] The element OperatingLeaseLiabilityNoncurrent with a value of 325,000,000 and the Balance Sheet Location Axis with the member us-gaap:OtherNoncurrentLiabilitiesMember only appears in the balance sheet line item represented by the member. The Balance Sheet Location Axis should be used when the OperatingLeaseLiabilityNoncurrent amount is split across multiple Balance Sheet line items. When the amount is not spread across multiple line items then the OperatingLeaseLiabilityNoncurrentStatementOfFinancialPositionExtensibleList item should be used with a value of the element name of the Balance Sheet line item.
